<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Marriage proposal | FIORE</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <!-- AOS Library CDN -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

  <!-- AOS Library JS -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.js"></script>
  <script>
    AOS.init({
      duration: 2500,  // Animation lasts for 2500 milliseconds
      delay: 300,      // Delay animation by 300 milliseconds before it starts
      once: true       // Ensures animations run only once (when scrolling down)
    });
  </script>

  <section class="proposal-hero">
    <div class="proposal-hero-content">
      <h1>Marriage Proposal</h1>
      <p>Love meets elegance in a proposal full of romance and charm.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="intro-section" data-aos="fade-up">
    <p>
      A marriage proposal is one of the most cherished moments in a couple’s journey — a magical chapter where love turns into a lifelong promise. A Marriage Proposal Party brings together the beauty of the question "Will you marry me?" with the joy of sharing that moment with loved ones in a thoughtfully planned celebration.
      At FIORE, we believe your proposal deserves more than just a simple setting — it deserves a dreamy backdrop, elegant décor, heartfelt details, and seamless coordination. Let us help you create a proposal party that’s as unique and unforgettable as the bond you share. 
    </p>
  </section>
  
  <section class="proposal-section">
    <div class="proposal-block" data-aos="fade-right">
      <img src="/img/mp-loc.jpg" alt="Romantic Proposal Location">
      <div>
        <h2>Scenic & Sentimental Location</h2>
        <p>Choose a breathtaking venue that holds sentimental value – be it a rooftop under the stars, a serene beach at sunset, or a candlelit garden. FIORE helps you transform any space into a magical moment.</p>
        <a href="/hotels" class="luxury-button">Explore Locations</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="proposal-block reverse" data-aos="fade-left">
      <img src="/img/mp-decor.jpg" alt="Luxurious Proposal Decor">
      <div>
        <h2>Elegant Decor Setup</h2>
        <p>Think floral arches, cascading fairy lights, and candle arrangements. Our decorators bring luxury aesthetics to life with personalized touches like your initials, timeline of love, or a rose-petal aisle.</p>
        <a href="/decorators" class="luxury-button">View Decor Options</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="proposal-block" data-aos="fade-right">
      <img src="/img/mp-dress.jpg" alt="Proposal Outfit Ideas">
      <div>
        <h2>Dress to Impress</h2>
        <p>For a glamorous reveal, dress in timeless fashion. From tailored tuxedos to flowing gowns, our stylists help create a look worthy of the big “Yes!”. Add matching accessories or a surprise detail for a wow effect.</p>
        <a href="/dresses" class="luxury-button">Get Styled</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="proposal-block reverse" data-aos="fade-left">
      <img src="/img/mp-photo.jpg" alt="Proposal Photographer">
      <div>
        <h2>Capture the Emotion</h2>
        <p>A professional photographer ensures no moment goes uncaptured — from the teary-eyed “yes” to the joyful post-proposal celebration. We offer cinematic edits for a keepsake you'll treasure forever.</p>
        <a href="/link_photographers" class="luxury-button">Book Photographer</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="proposal-block" data-aos="fade-right">
      <img src="/img/mn-table.png" alt="Celebration After the Proposal">
      <div>
        <h2>Post-Proposal Celebration</h2>
        <p>Invite family and friends to join you moments after the proposal for a surprise afterparty with champagne toasts, music, and personalized favors.</p>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
